comment.author: 37377809@N00
comment._content: Yes, I love Paul's stuff. And I really like the idea of crowd sourcing untagged photos and getting that info back to the institution.  There will definitely be an open API, but we will all need to confab more to figure out a seamless 2 way street model.  Also, we don't want to just take away from the community and dialogue at the Commons, for instance, but there is also a vast expanse of commons-type content out on other sites.  Finding dynamic ways to bring it all together is pretty exciting.
